comment_data.body:
i think the switch case is worse :) 3 assignments instead of one assignment:

```c
  void *ctx = NULL;
  switch (scope) {
  case kOptScopeWin:
    ctx = &switchwin; break;
  case kOptScopeBuf:
    ctx = &aco; break;
  case kOptScopeTab:
    ctx = &swtab; break;
  case kOptScopeGlobal:
    break;
  }
```

